{"tid":446332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞法師表演「蒸活人」期間疑心臟病發 悶在鍋裡喪命","createTime":"2017-10-24T08:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T16:23:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"e978458d9cdc3c7d55007612172de825115ee0f1","tid":446332,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n手上的玉米跟壽桃都蒸熟了，但這位馬來西亞法師林文華仍好端端坐在鍋內毫髮無傷，這個長達75分鐘的「蒸活人」表演讓林文華聲名大噪。沒想到近日法師在家鄉再次表演此神功時，疑似心臟病發昏迷於鍋內，儘管趕緊救出來，不久後他仍斷氣喪命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/10/24/1106770-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F1106770-XXL.jpg&h=0884d320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林文華在鍋內已昏迷。（圖／翻攝自Oriental Daily News Malaysia YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，林文華從17歲時，就參與許多法會神功表演，直到2013年他為配合盂蘭超渡法會，進行75分鐘的「蒸活人」表演，儘管手上的玉米熟透了，林文華卻只流一身汗，神奇功力讓他名聲揚名海外。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到已69歲的他卻意外喪命，23日林文華要配合九皇大帝慶典，在吉打州（Kedah）的清龍宮再度表演「蒸活人」。當天他穿著乩童肚兜，並盤腿坐在爐灶上，再用巨大鍋蓋蓋上，而一旁工作人員不斷添加柴火，以讓爐火燒的更旺。<br />\n<br />\n未料表演進行到30分鐘左右，工作人員就從鍋內就聽到拍打聲，趕緊打開鍋蓋時，林文華已昏迷癱軟，工作人員將他抬到地上，不久後就斷氣身亡。據瞭解，林文華疑似心臟病發，他2年前曾接受心臟冠狀動脈搭橋手術（CABG），甚至有輕微中風。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDLyIaM1xRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDLyIaM1xRE&d=HdUXrYEkG2fOkZ1wUI3%2FRDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f992674b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDLyIaM1xRE</a><br />\n▲影片來源：YouTube，若遭移除請見諒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=307625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D307625&d=HdUXrYEkG2fOkZ1wUI3%2FRDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=13773ae2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D307625&h=acd1d6e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=307625</a>"},{"pid":"4f3c3556549d396c91095cb8f99797f7e9d115f2","tid":446332,"uid":19501,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038312867ea4597798f7270163e28c236887603e","tid":446332,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"悶死"},{"pid":"3d1e698bdf620664fd01ccf4942ad00da10b8f7b","tid":446332,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"馬拉果班轉數係福建 客家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198ac75e40d315ce64d1d8dbd447f2b172718055","tid":446332,"uid":60655,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"焗桑拿都可以拎黎做表演？"},{"pid":"02aba2e5867d0942213cd27a45dd4f8c6914ce19","tid":446332,"uid":63950,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55779bafb5223b14b56b425f843a078c10906a2d","tid":446332,"uid":68079,"like":1,"dislike":68,"score":-67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係條橫丫腸突然間發炎一痛 個信念一鬆嘅時候 熟咗</blockquote><br />\n乾珅一開 七色氣流一轉 開哂佢"},{"pid":"83327184f78cc4bddea6a3ca2636b32a47840685","tid":446332,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"Darwinism <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf97879d0e298658a2912492090a20e5eb116dc","tid":446332,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"表演成功"},{"pid":"b7ebb8253e7481555316c9f147d0f57583ef81ba","tid":446332,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:41:35.000Z"